  (text "Drive current note: each side is two motors in parallel, about 3A stall at 6V reference. 2S LiHV direct drive increases current and heating; avoid long stalls and use WEKA current/thermal protection as margin, not as normal operation. Motor-output input wiring at J22 must use the solder-pad footprint and 20 AWG or better flexible wire."
    (at 15.00 121.00 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.05 1.05)) (justify left top))
